{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u25c6Game Description:</h2>&quot;SETTRIS&quot; is a block-arranging puzzle game in which the player fits pieces of various shapes into empty squares on the puzzle board, and fills all empty squares to clear the board.<br>The player must rotate and flip the pieces to fit them together and successfully place them in the right order. Sometimes you may have to try a new approach to solve the puzzle, such as removing all the pieces.<br>There is no time limit, so you can take your time to solve the puzzle.<br>Relax and enjoy the puzzle in the sea.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u25c6Two game modes are available!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Stage Mode</strong><br>In this mode, the game is cleared when all the squares on the puzzle board on the stage are filled.<br>The difficulty level increases with each new stage.<br></li><li><strong>Time Attack Mode</strong><br>This is a game mode in which players compete to see how many puzzle pieces they can solve within a time limit.<br>The pieces distributed are designed to fill all empty squares on the puzzle board.<br>The number of pieces that appear changes depending on the stage, and the number of pieces increases as the difficulty level increases.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to SETTRIS","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2297230/a286438f02000c0d035a839023a1632cff0a6db1.jpg"},{"name":"Puzzle Beginner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2297230/d38bba7eaf8be8f3ee157812abe6f01fdab79c22.jpg"},{"name":"Puzzle Intermediate","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2297230/0c04f8a6cd19b7e92b040938e0deef896568c8a6.jpg"},{"name":"Puzzle Advanced","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2297230/31670af2e1bfc4593031252a3937cd4829e1d998.jpg"},{"name":"Puzzle Expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcomm